          <span>Chemicals</span>
          <span>Rentals</span>
        </div>

        <div class="features row">
          <div class="block col-md-4 col-10">
            <div class="chead"><i class="fa fa-dollar fa-lg"></i></div>
            <div class="cbody">
              <h5>â‚¹ 40k + Revenue</h5>
              <p>Company had over 40, 000 revenue in the past months</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="block col-md-4 col-10">
            <div class="chead"><i class="fa fa-star fa-lg"></i></div>
            <div class="cbody">
              <h5>Venture Backed</h5>
              <p>Company is backed by a venture firm</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="points mx-md-5">
          <h3>What they stand for :</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Magni,
              laboriosam.
            </li>
            <li>Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing.</li>
            <li>
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
              Voluptatibus, voluptates? Omnis!
            </li>
            <li>
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Laborum
              nisi doloribus eius commodi. Minus culpa nulla delectus dolore
              fugit praesentium.
            </li>
            <li>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="#"><button class="deal-btn">View Deal</button></a>
        <img src="/images/newsletter.jpg" alt="newsletter" />
        <p class="info-1">
          <a href="https://pepcorns.com/#!/knowledgebase/investors"
            >Learn how to invest in car renting project here >></a
          >
        </p>
        <p class="info-2">
          If you've never invested in a startup before, checkout our knowledge
          base. Investing in private companies is very difficult than the stock
          market.
        </p>
      </div>

      <%- include('footer') -%>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
